# This project does NOT use .env files.
# All configuration is fetched from AWS SSM Parameter Store at runtime.
#
# Required SSM parameters (path: /banyan/hasura/):
#
# engine-url          — ALB URL of remote Hasura engine (e.g., http://<alb-dns>)
# admin-secret        — Hasura admin secret (SecureString)
# db-connection-uri   — RDS PostgreSQL connection string (SecureString)
# ndc-connector-url   — NDC connector internal URL
# metadata-s3-bucket  — S3 bucket for metadata storage (used by deploy)
# ecs-cluster         — ECS cluster name (used by deploy)
# ecs-engine-service  — ECS engine service name (used by deploy)
#
# Ensure your AWS credentials are configured:
#   AWS_PROFILE=banyan bun run hasura:start
